#compdef stf
# ============================================================================
# _stf — zsh completion for **stf** — openstf/stf (the **Smartphone
#         Test Farm** — DeviceFarmer/STF), the canonical open-source
#         **Android device farm** control plane.  STF lets you
#         control an entire rack of physical Android devices from a
#         web browser:  real-time screen mirroring (~30-60 fps via
#         minicap), input injection (keyboard + touch + multi-touch
#         + accelerometer + rotation + GPS spoofing via the bundled
#         `STFService.apk` and `minitouch` companion binaries),
#         ADB-shell tunneling, app installs from local `.apk` or
#         remote URLs, automated test fixture orchestration via
#         Appium / WebDriverIO / Detox / Espresso / UiAutomator2,
#         long-lived user-session bookings + group-based access
#         control + per-device usage analytics, all driven by a
#         **distributed microservice architecture** of 28 individual
#         unit processes that the `stf <unit-name>` CLI surface
#         launches independently.  TS-Node=171 CLOSING leg of Axis
#         116 (LDAP / RFC-4511 directory access protocol) at 1/1/1
#         with TRIPLE-171 landmark + 109th Axis closed via the
#         canonical Node.js LDAP library **ldapjs**.
# ============================================================================
